\f3\b\fs28 FORUM
\f2\b0\fs24 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs28 \cf0 A place where people can discuss questions and issues with the project.
\fs24 \

\fs28 Onboarding / forum connected to platform choice eg: github has issues management and tracking included. If people have trouble making the thing, how to suggest improvements, track changes, bugs.
\fs24 \

\fs28 \
\pard\pardeftab720\li1800\fi-720\ri-618\partightenfactor0
