\f2\fs24 \cf0  2.2.	
\f3\b\fs28 READ ONLY
\f2\b0\fs24 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs28 \cf0 Generate READ ONLY output files on each platform to visualize the project. Give people access to VIEW and use the project without making modifications or changes. Ability to READ across platforms to view, without having to use proprietary software.
\fs24 \

\fs28 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf0 OPTIONAL:
\f1\b0\fs24 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs28 \cf0 Provide a development branch for people trying new features.
\fs24 \

\fs28 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf0 Each Release provides better reference and enables people to fork (multiple sub streams and variations of the project) and improve your outcome, spread the word and gain new resources and users.
\f1\b0\fs24 \

\f0\b\fs28 \
\pard\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-360\ri-618\partightenfactor0
