\f2\b0\fs24 \cf0  3.	
\f3\b\fs28 Source
\f2\b0\fs24 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs28 \cf0 Share your source files as soon as possible! Original content files, text, sources are essential from the beginning to help understand what you\'92re doing and with the process of documentation itself.
\fs24 \

\fs28 \
Anything READ ONLY is NOT a source file! Don\'92t make people reverse engineer your work to create or adapt something new.
\fs24 \

\fs28 \
Keep in mind that Git based systems don\'92t work well with big sized binary files (videos, large photos or PDFs, etc.), you might upload them somewhere else and share the download link.
\fs24 \

\fs28 \
\pard\pardeftab720\li1800\fi-720\ri-618\partightenfactor0
